        id: 49,
        author: "Pankaj Nath",
        title: `Five foods that help you remain fit, healthy and active`,
        img: "https://english.cdn.zeenews.com/sites/default/files/2017/02/15/571411-untitled-1.jpg",
        description: `In today's world we have to be fit and healthy in order cope with the ever-mounting pressures of a globalised life.`,
        category: "Food",
